    <exercise id="fs-id2404351" type="conceptual-questions"><problem id="fs-id2660428"><para id="import-auto-id693773">Do you feel yourself thrown to either side when you negotiate a curve that is ideally banked for your car's speed? What is the direction of the force exerted on you by the car seat?</para>    </problem></exercise>
