      <para id="fs-id1436140">(b) What is the centripetal acceleration at the edge of the tire?</para>
      <para id="fs-id1486366">(c) With what force must a determined <m:math><m:semantics><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mtext>00</m:mtext><m:mo stretchy="false">×</m:mo><m:msup><m:mtext>10</m:mtext><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mo stretchy="false">−</m:mo><m:mtext>15</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:msup><m:mspace width="0.25em"/><m:mtext>kg</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow><m:mrow/></m:mrow><m:annotation encoding="StarMath 5.0"> size 12{1 "." "00" times "10" rSup { size 8{ - "15"} } } {}</m:annotation></m:semantics></m:math> bacterium cling to the rim?</para><para id="fs-id2400686">(d) Take the ratio of this force to the bacterium's weight.</para>
